data.title: Imidacloprid Technical Fact Sheet
data.text:
Inhalation LC50 Up to and including 0.05 mg/L

(>2.0 mg/L) Primary Eye Irritation Corrosive (irreversible destruction of ocular tissue) or corneal involvement or irritation persisting for more than 21 days Corneal involvement or other eye irritation clearing in 8 - 21 days Corneal involvement or other eye irritation clearing in 7 days or less Minimal effects clearing in less than 24 hours
